'''叶附生苔'''，或稱'''葉附生苔類植物'''，是指[[附生|附生]]于活的[[维管植物|维管植物]]叶片表面的[[苔蘚植物|苔蘚植物]]<ref>{{ cite journal | authors = Malombe, I.; Matheka, K. W.; Pócs, T.; Patiño, J. | title = Edge effect on epiphyllous bryophytes in Taita Hills fragmented afromontane forests | journal = ''Journal of Bryology'' | year = 2016 | volume = 38 | issue = 1 | pages = 33-46 | issn = 0373-6687 | doi = 10.1179/1743282015Y.0000000015 | url = }}</ref>，其中絕大多數屬於[[地錢門|地錢門]][[細鱗蘚科|細鱗蘚科]]，也有少部分是[[苔類植物門|苔類植物門]]、[[角蘚門|角蘚門]]或其他地錢門的成員<ref>{{cite journal | authors = Gradstein, S. R. | title = The taxonomic diversity of epiphyllous bryophytes | journal = ''Abstracta Botanica'' | year = 1997 | volume = 21 | issue = 1 | pages = 15-19 | issn = 0133-6215 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/285697894_The_taxonomic_diversity_of_epiphyllous_bryophytes | access-date = 2020-12-15 | archive-date = 2017-03-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170313221734/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/285697894_The_taxonomic_diversity_of_epiphyllous_bryophytes | dead-url = no }}</ref>。葉附生苔在[[南極洲|南極洲]]以外的各大[[洲|洲]]都有分布<ref>{{cite journal | authors = Tang, X.; Gradstein, S. R.; Sun, L.-W.; Zhu, M.-J.; Shi, R.-P.; Wei, Q.-Q.; Chen, Y.-Q.; Zhou, X.-X.; Wang, J. | title = A contribution to the knowledge of epiphyllous bryophytes in Tianmushan National Nature Reserve (Zhejiang, China), with remarks on climate warming and nature conservation | journal = ''Lindbergia'' | year = 2018 | volume = 41 | issue = 1 | pages = 01103 | url = https://bioone.org/journals/lindbergia/volume-41/issue-1/linbg.01103/A-contribution-to-the-knowledge-of-epiphyllous-bryophytes-in-Tianmushan/10.25227/linbg.01103.full#bibr08 | doi = 10.25227/linbg.01103 | access-date = 2020-12-15 | archive-date = 2021-01-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210115145759/https://bioone.org/journals/lindbergia/volume-41/issue-1/linbg.01103/A-contribution-to-the-knowledge-of-epiphyllous-bryophytes-in-Tianmushan/10.25227/linbg.01103.full#bibr08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但在[[熱帶|熱帶]]至[[副熱帶|副熱帶]]的[[熱帶雨林|熱帶雨林]]和[[季風雨林|季風雨林]]中尤其繁盛<ref name = Chen1964>{{ cite journal | author1 = 陈邦杰 | coauthors = 吴鹏程 | title = 中国叶附生苔类植物的研究(一) | journal = 植物分类学报 | year = 1964 | volume = 9 | issue = 3 | pages = 213-276 | issn = 1674-4918 | url = https://www.jse.ac.cn/fileup/1674-4918/PDF/1964-3-213-16704.pdf }}</ref>，在多樣性高的區域甚至可見數十種不同的葉附生苔棲息於同一片葉子上<ref>{{ cite journal | author = Lücking, A. | title = Diversity and distribution of epiphyllous bryophytes in a tropical rainforest in Costa Rica | journal = ''Abstracta Botanica'' | year = 1997 | volume = 21 | issue = 1 | pages = 79-87 | issn = 0133-6215 | doi = | url = }}</ref>；在其餘地區，葉附生苔則極其罕見<ref>{{ cite journal | author = Porley, R. D. | title = Foliicolous ''Metzgeria fruticulosa'' on Box leaves in the Chiltern Hills, England | journal = ''Journal of Bryology'' | year = 1996 | volume = 19 | issue = 1 | pages = 188-189 | issn = 0373-6687 | doi = 10.1179/jbr.1996.19.1.188 }}</ref>。

叶附生苔的个体细小扁平，腹面有束状[[假根|假根]]和卷曲的囊状腹瓣，有些叶附生苔[[细胞壁|细胞壁]]表面突起成疣状<ref>{{cite journal | authors = Bai, Y.; Chen, S.; Qian, H.; Yu, S.; Xu, Y.; Zhang, Z.; Shen, C. Chen, Y.; Zhang, M.; Yu, J.; Zhu, R. | title = Species diversity of epiphyllous liverworts in Qianjiangyuan National Park, Zhejiang | journal = ''Biodiversity Science'' | year = 2020 | volume = 28 | issue = 2 | pages = 231-237 | issn = 1005-0094 | doi = 10.17520/biods.2019273 | url = https://www.biodiversity-science.net/EN/10.17520/biods.2019273 | access-date = 2020-12-15 | archive-date = 2020-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201025100218/http://www.biodiversity-science.net/EN/10.17520/biods.2019273 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。由於葉片的壽命不長，能讓葉附生苔落腳的時間相當短，故這類苔蘚植物發展出高度特化的生活史，如高度依賴[[芽胞|芽胞]]（brood body）、[[繁殖枝|繁殖枝]]、脫落的葉等[[無性繁殖|無性繁殖]]機制<ref>{{ cite book | author = Zhu, R.-L.; So, M. L. | title = ''Epiphyllous Liverworts of China'' | publisher = J. Cramer | location = Berlin | isbn = 978-3-443-51043-5 | year = 2001 }}</ref>，孢子採行{{le|早發性萌芽|Germination#Precocious germination}}，[[配子體|配子體]]有[[幼態延續|幼態發育]]（neotenic development）現象，以及快速形成{{le|配子囊|Gametangium}}等等，以達到短時間內大量播遷的效果<ref>{{ cite journal | author = Alvarenga, L. D. P.; Pôrto, K. C.; Zartman, C. E. | title = Sex ratio, spatial segregation, and fertilization rates of the epiphyllous moss ''Crossomitrium patrisiae'' (Brid.) Müll.Hal. in the Brazilian Atlantic rainforest | journal = ''Journal of Bryology'' | year = 2013 | volume = 35 | issue = 2 | pages = 88-95 | issn = 0373-6687 | doi = 10.1179/174328213X13662092820316 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/272251364_Sex_ratio_spatial_segregation_and_fertilization_rates_of_the_epiphyllous_moss_Crossomitrium_patrisiae_Brid_MullHal_in_the_Brazilian_Atlantic_rainforest }}</ref>。迄今並未發現葉附生苔對於宿主植物的種類或葉片形態表現出專一性<ref>{{cite journal | author = Benavides, J. C.; Sastre-De Jesús, I. | title = Diversity and Rarity of Epiphyllous Bryophytes in a Superhumid Tropical Lowland Forest of Chocó-Colombia | journal = ''Cryptogamie, Bryologie'' | year = 2011 | volume = 32 | issue = 2 | pages = 119-133 | issn = 1290-0796 | doi = 10.7872/cryb.v32.iss1.2011.119 | url = http://sciencepress.mnhn.fr/en/periodiques/bryologie/32/2/diversity-and-rarity-epiphyllous-bryophytes-superhumid-tropical-lowland-forest-choco-colombia | access-date = 2020-12-15 | archive-date = 2020-09-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200925133544/http://sciencepress.mnhn.fr/en/periodiques/bryologie/32/2/diversity-and-rarity-epiphyllous-bryophytes-superhumid-tropical-lowland-forest-choco-colombia | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但已知其偏好附生於常綠、硬革質、較光滑且較厚的葉片，如[[殼斗科|殼斗科]]、[[茶科|茶科]]、[[茜草科|茜草科]]、[[蘭科|蘭科]]、[[蕁麻科|蕁麻科]]、[[蕨類|蕨類]]等<ref name = Chen1964/><ref>{{ cite journal | author = 姜炎彬, 邵小明 | title = 叶附生苔植物物种多样性分布格局及生态成因 | journal = 植物生态学报 | year = 2016 | volume = 40 | issue = 5 | pages = 523-532 | issn = 1005-264X | doi = 10.17521/cjpe.2015.0359 | url = https://www.plant-ecology.com/article/2016/1005-264X/1005-264X-40-5-523.shtml }}</ref>。

